1.安装nginx
sudo apt update
sudo apt install nginx
sudo systemctl status nginx

2.nginx配置
在/etc/nginx/sites-available下新建一个配置文件xxx.conf
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name cloud.marwen.buzz;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:9000;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
    }
}

3.创建一个符号链接，指向站点启用目录中创建的配置文件。
sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/cloud.marwen.buzz.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/

4.测试重启nginx
sudo nginx -t
sudo systemctl reload nginx

5.启动python静态服务器，在9000端口
